            . I am a <rs id="t18221204-127-viclabel657" type="occupation">grocer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-127-victim1140 t18221204-127-viclabel657"></join>, and live in Bishopsgate-street. On the 11th of November, about a quarter before three o'clock, I was in a crowd in the <placeName id="t18221204-127-crimeloc658">City-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18221204-127-crimeloc658" type="placeName" value="City-road"></interp>
