                     <interp inst="t18221204-127-person1144" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner at the gentleman's pocket; he took the handkerchief out, and put it in his breast.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I just went into the crowd; the handkerchief was between me and the gentleman.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
